Package: rozofs-metadata-backup
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
		 ${misc:Depends},
		 pv,
		 tar (>= 1.26),
		 time
Description: RozoFS metadata backup utility
 rozofs-metadata backup is a utility to backup all rozofs metadata to
 another filesystem (useful only when the HA is dead). This backup is
 made with tar and compressed with gzip. Backups could be schedule
 automatically with the rozofs-metadata-backup systemd timer. 
 .
 RozoFS is a scale-out distributed network POSIX file system using erasure
 coding and Mojette Transform algorithm for data distribution. RozoFS
 designed to provide very high availability levels with optimized raw
 capacity usage on heterogeneous commodity hardware
